### Configuration API Tests
### Tests for ConfigurationController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get project configuration
### Returns the current project configuration settings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/config/project
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update project configuration
### Patch update for project configuration settings
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/config/project
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": {
    "name": "opencode"
  },
  "model": "glm-4.7"
}

###

### Get global configuration
### Returns global OpenCode server configuration
GET http://localhost:8080/api/config/global
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get available providers configuration
### Returns list of available AI providers and their configurations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/config/providers
Content-Type: application/json

###
